                        <div id="page-title">
                            中国分部异常项目
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><strong>前言：</strong>SCP基金会中国分部发现了为数不少的项目无用而不值得进一步关注。本文件列出了那些激起了一些好奇心的项目。如果这些项目的知识在将来变得有用或必要，则可以将其作为一种资源。<br />
— █████博士，Site-CN-██研究主管</p>
<p>欲查看已归档的异常项目记录，请<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn-arc">点击这里</a>。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button create-button" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00524/parentPage/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/#_editpage">添加新的记录</a></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<p style="text-align: center;">显示顺序：<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating%20desc">评分较高</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating">评分较低</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name">最早发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name%20desc">最新发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/random">随机</a></p>
<p><strong>提示：</strong>如果你希望改变你的评分，请先点击“X”取消你的评分，再重新评分。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00513/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>项目为<span class="animation-1">一</span>。</p>
<p><strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██</p>
<p><strong>回收地点：</strong>SCiPNet主数据库</p>
<p><strong>当前状态：</strong>未收容</p>
<p><strong>实例：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;展开</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;收合</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style="height: 20em; width: calc(100% - 4px)"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>笔记：</strong>即日起<span class="animation-2">禁止</span>。——主管Hormress</p>



<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00513" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00513" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00513-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4142571&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247359" alt="Dr Hormress" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4142571)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;">Dr Hormress</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1609587134 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">02 Jan 2021 11:32</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00475/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<div class="textchange">

<div class="sitemember">
<p><span style="color: blue">游客</span></p>
</div>
</div>



<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00475" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00475" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00475-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenno-215" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6704451); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6704451&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247359" alt="tenno-215" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6704451)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenno-215" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6704451); return false;">tenno-215</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1607170512 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">05 Dec 2020 12:15</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00400/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一颗无论用什么方式都无法让其进入篮筐的篮球。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-01与Site-CN-02友谊篮球赛赛场。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>在比赛时一名队员尝试球不离开手强行塞入篮筐<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-741352-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-741352-1')">1</a></sup>时爆炸。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>这个球是Site-CN-01与Site-CN-02友谊篮球赛时Site-CN-01在领先时Site-CN-01要求换的球。要不是这个知道这个消息，我都怀疑人生了。</em>——Site-CN-02尝试扣篮的球员</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00400" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00400" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00400-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tian-xiu233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6240575); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6240575&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247359" alt="tian xiu233" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6240575)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tian-xiu233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6240575); return false;">tian xiu233</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1600595491 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">20 Sep 2020 09:51</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="title">脚注</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-741352-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-741352-1')">1</a>. 又名扣篮。</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00397/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一本出版社，印刷时间均不详的《克苏鲁神话》文本，具有异常模因效应，使任何阅读者坚信书中所述为真实事件。记忆清除被发现可以清除模因影响。中国████市监狱内██名因“邪教活动”而入狱的囚犯被证明与该物件有关。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>中国████市一处“克苏鲁异教”活动现场<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存在Site-CN-██的低价值物品保存区<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>基金会怎么不派人去南极?-Dr.Li</em><br />
<em>去那干嘛？-Dr.Huang</em><br />
<em>收容修格斯啊。-Dr.Li</em><br />
<em>啊？？！！-Dr.Huang</em></p>
